This topic describes how to use Pivotal Operations Manager to configure the BOSH Director on Azure Government Cloud.

First, complete the steps in [Preparing to Deploy Ops Manager on Azure](./prepare-env-manual.html) and [Deploying Ops Manager on Azure](./deploy-manual.html).

Then, follow the procedure for a manual Azure install. In the procedure, select **Azure Government Cloud** in the **Azure Environment** dropdown and set custom VM types.

For the installation procedure, see [Configuring BOSH Director on Azure](config-manual.html).
